The actors and crew of Anand Tiwari‚Äôs rom-com movie are shooting a romantic song in Croatia currently. Amidst the magical beauty of Croatia and the pristine blue waters, the outcome of the shooting will surely be breathtaking and blissful. Farah Khan is also working on this project and making it super successful. She posted a beautiful photo on her Instagram story with the newest duo of Bollywood and we are totally gushing over the photo. Farah captioned it, ‚ÄòRocking the boat‚Äô. Also read: Katrina Kaif Shares Throwback Pictures Of Maldives Trip With Husband Vicky Kaushal It seems that Farah herself is charmed by the aura of Croatia. She also posted her solo picture in Croatia on Instagram and captioned it, ‚ÄòCroatia needs no filter.. can‚Äôt wait to shoot here..‚Äô. Well, we can completely agree with what Farah said. Croatia surely does not need any filter, such is its charisma.

 

